      <hedline>
        <hl1>Swissair Worktime Cut</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">AP</byline>
      <dateline>ZURICH, Feb. 15</dateline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Swissair, faced with a drop in bookings because of the Persian Gulf war, said this week that its employees would be put on reduced working hours next month in a cost-cutting move. The action, which is the first such move in the Swiss flag carrier's 60-year history, will affect about 20,000 employees starting in mid-March.</p>
      </block>
